song_lyrics: Bāy grahī chhe re ho vā’le, karuṇā karī Naṭvar dharmalāle °ṭek
Have nahī koīnī re oshiyāḷī, shir par Viṭhṭhalvar vanmāḷī... ° 1
Bhav Brahmānā re ho Swāmī, mujane maḷiyā antarjāmī... ° 2
Gher gher lokaḍā re ho kahe chhe, meṇu dharmanā Nandannu de chhe... ° 3
Lāj nav manmā re ho āṇu, atishe bhāgya bhalu karī jāṇu... ° 4
Koī vidh na rahī re ho khāmī, maḷiyā Muktānandnā Swāmī... ° 5
title: Bāy grahī chhe re ho vā’le
